{
  "stem": "3690.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he wasn't satisfied with that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he picked up a big bottle of Korbel champagne and hit me about five, six times in the head and completely busted my skull.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it bent my brain inside my head.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the ambulance came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The fire department came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the police came and took me to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was very badly beaten up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was black and blue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My eyes, my ears, everything was swollen from the damage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the doctors couldn't believe this, I'm going to get out of it, because I was brain-damaged.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brain was bent inside my head.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so, but I-- three or four days later, I went back to work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Six months later, I got hold up again, and I got shot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the bullet went right through me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A guy shot me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that time, I made up my mind, I've got to get out of that business.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got out of the liquor business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went in the real estate business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I have bought apartments and houses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, since then, I'm still in the real estate business.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To my grandchildren?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CRYING] I like to tell them this, they should be good citizens.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and-- and-- and they should take-- strive to have a very good education, because the education is a very, very important thing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they should try to keep and stay in their Judaism and-- and-- and-- be a-- a-- an example for the other people in the world as what people can do after all this horrible things, what people go through and suffer.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and-- and they should try to be charitable and-- and-- and be nice to-- to all different people, nations, and-- and not to make hatred.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
